      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774847221548,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "0. Find use cases from feature docs:-\n    Functional Requirements:-\n        -> Search movies by city.\n        -> View Movie Details.\n        -> View Shows of a movie.\n        -> Select a Show\n        -> Lock Seats.\n        -> Create Booking.\n        -> Make Payment\n        -> Confirm Booking\n        -> Initiate Payment\n        -> Handle Payment Success\n        -> Handle Payment Failures\n        -> Retry Payments\n        -> Cancel Booking\n        -> Refund Payment\n        -> Release Seats\n        -> Send Booking Confirmation\n        -> Send Payment status\n\n    Non-Functional Requirements:-\n        -> High Availability\n        -> High Concurrency(10^3 users booking for same seat.)\n        -> Low Latency\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 17.93595206640229,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "0. Find use cases from feature docs:-\n    Functional Requirements:-\n        -> Search movies by city.\n        -> View Movie Details.\n        -> View Shows of a movie.\n        -> Select a Show\n        -> Lock Seats.\n        -> Create Booking.\n        -> Make Payment\n        -> Confirm Booking\n        -> Initiate Payment\n        -> Handle Payment Success\n        -> Handle Payment Failures\n        -> Retry Payments\n        -> Cancel Booking\n        -> Refund Payment\n        -> Release Seats\n        -> Send Booking Confirmation\n        -> Send Payment status\n\n    Non-Functional Requirements:-\n        -> High Availability\n        -> High Concurrency(10^3 users booking for same seat.)\n        -> Low Latency\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
