    {
      "id": "U0P2_nN1jrNhSgNOwj6xC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 217.88504224084693,
      "y": 1146.66015625,
      "width": 1417.3342811327957,
      "height": 420,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 315654129,
      "version": 2059,
      "versionNonce": 511233009,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774934282035,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Determine Invariants \n    -> User -> Select City→ Select show → Select Theatre -> Select seats → Lock seats → Create booking → Pay → Confirm booking\n\n    -> Invariants Related to Seats:-\n        -> A user cannot select a locked seat.\n        -> Two/Many Users cannot be allocated same seat in a particular show.\n        ->  Wrong seat number cannot be allocated.\n    -> Invariants related to Theatres:-\n        -> Theatres must be listed according to city selected.\n    -> Invariants related to SeatLock:-\n        -> A seatLock must expire after TTL.\n    -> Invariants related top Bookings\n        -> A booking must have 1 show.\n        -> A confirm booking must have successful payment [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n        -> booking should not be allowed after the start of show. [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n    -> Inavriants related to Payments:-\n        -> Booking amount should always be equal to payment amount.[Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n        -> On payment failure, should be able to retry payment.\n        -> On Payment Failure must relaese locks. [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n    \n ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Determine Invariants \n    -> User -> Select City→ Select show → Select Theatre -> Select seats → Lock seats → Create booking → Pay → Confirm booking\n\n    -> Invariants Related to Seats:-\n        -> A user cannot select a locked seat.\n        -> Two/Many Users cannot be allocated same seat in a particular show.\n        ->  Wrong seat number cannot be allocated.\n    -> Invariants related to Theatres:-\n        -> Theatres must be listed according to city selected.\n    -> Invariants related to SeatLock:-\n        -> A seatLock must expire after TTL.\n    -> Invariants related top Bookings\n        -> A booking must have 1 show.\n        -> A confirm booking must have successful payment [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n        -> booking should not be allowed after the start of show. [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n    -> Inavriants related to Payments:-\n        -> Booking amount should always be equal to payment amount.[Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n        -> On payment failure, should be able to retry payment.\n        -> On Payment Failure must relaese locks. [Cross Aggregate Invariants]\n    \n ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
